highlights.text: “Espresso” by Sabrina Carpenter is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Israel, up 81 spots at #60.
Omer Adam has the most spots on Top Songs Israel. “רק שלך” is the highest at #1.

“לשוב הביתה” by Ishay Ribo has been on Top Songs Israel the longest, at 320 weeks straight.
